Finally, someone who can get this far!
This is the Forest of the Saints, the deepest part.。
I'm so proud of you for coming here by yourself.。
It looks healthy, soft, just the way I like it!
I can't take it anymore!　Let's eat!
Oh, my God! What are you doing?　It's cold!
And then suddenly you're treating people like food.
You're covering your legs, but they know.
Oh, I see you're studying hard.。
Smart kids need to taste their food.
If you don't want to be stiffed, go through here!
I don't want to fight for nothing.。
Is that what you're saying to me?
Isn't it you who's out of control and being eaten one way or the other?
If that's the case, why don't you just try to hit me with that magic instead of avoiding it?
You won't get more than frostbite!
That's all I need to know.。
Wait a minute. Of course I'll let you through.。
Do you know where we are?
What?　I don't know. That's why I'm here, but...
So, you're just gonna let me do this for no reason...
What would happen to a demon that was trying to eat you one way or the other?
Would you like to know again?
This forest lost its efficacy decades ago.
Still, the humans claimed it as a sacred spot.
He was inviting guests to the local town and warming their pockets.。
This selfish human behavior angered the predecessor fairies.
The humans have been thoroughly eliminated from this forest.。
And yet, humans, when restrained, become even more stubborn.
They're trying to get into this forest.。
That's why you need a man-eating monster like me.
I put him there as a guardian.。
If the person who entered disappears, the humans will be scared.
You didn't think they'd come in, did you?。
You saw those fairies, didn't you?
I've learned to take pleasure in eliminating humans.
It's not even close to being a fairy. It's a monster.。
But I love humans, okay?　They're delicious.。
Especially for a young man like you.。
I'm sorry you didn't get to eat.。
And this is not a place for humans to be.
This spring is just a puddle.。
After you've seen the sights, get the hell out of here.。
There's nothing in the lake anymore, I'm sorry to say.。
Can you just leave me with one arm, please?
I haven't eaten a young woman in years.
Yada, it's got an upper body similar to a human's.
Why don't you just eat your own arm?。
・・・・・・・・・ Well, there's the rub...
I was about to be convinced!　I like you too.
You were never born a Lamia!
Damn it!　If I have to go through this...
I should have been in a more lily-livered game!
Next time I see you, I'm going to eat you for sure!。
I'm just going to tickle you again!。
You're weaker than I thought, my dear.。
If you like this sort of thing, you'll enjoy it more, okay?
Come here, come here, come here.
I don't want any more pain!
The letters are covered in moss and unreadable...
but there are newly dug letters at the bottom.。
Imperfect magic, depending on the ability of the wielder.
It has the potential to be reborn anew...
When thou askest, the young tree shall also answer thee.
